org.jetel.data.primitive

Class CloverLong

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • org.jetel.data.primitive.CloverLong
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Numeric

    public final class CloverLong
extends java.lang.Number
implements Numeric
    A class that represents a long integer value.
    It is anologous java.lang.Long class but is mutable. You can change value during all live cycle of this object.
    Since:
    December 2, 2005
    See Also:
    CloverInteger, CloverDouble, Serialized Form
